Field Documentation

UInt32 Vps_DssDispcOvlyPanelConfig::alphaBlenderEnable

Selects the alpha blender overlay manager for the output instead of the color key alpha blende. TODO - This is depreciated, Check if we need to have this variable.

UInt32 Vps_DssDispcOvlyPanelConfig::backGroundColor

24-bit RGB color value to specify the default background color. 31--—24 23--—16 15---—8 7----—0 Unused R G B.

UInt32 Vps_DssDispcOvlyPanelConfig::colorKeyEnable

Enable or Disable the transparence Color Key.

UInt32 Vps_DssDispcOvlyPanelConfig::colorKeySel

Transparence Color Key Selection. For valid values check Vps_DssDispcTransColorKeySel.

Int32 Vps_DssDispcOvlyPanelConfig::deltaLinesPerPanel

Delta Size value of the bottom field compared to top field.

UInt32 Vps_DssDispcOvlyPanelConfig::ovlyOptimization

Overlay Optimization for the overlay. For valid values check Vps_DssDispcOvlyOptimization.

UInt32 Vps_DssDispcOvlyPanelConfig::transColorKey

Transparence color key value in RGB format. [0] BITMAP 1 (CLUT), [23,1] set to 0's [1:0] BITMAP 2 (CLUT), [23,2] set to 0's [3:0] BITMAP 4 (CLUT), [23,4] set to 0's [7:0] BITMAP 8 (CLUT), [23,8] set to 0's [11:0] RGB 12, [23,12] set to 0's 24--—12 11--—8 7---—4 3----—0 Zero R G B [15:0] RGB 16, [23,16] set to 0's ?????????????????????????????????? Unused R G B [23:0] RGB 24 - (RW) 23--—16-15---—8-7----—0 R G B.

UInt32 Vps_DssDispcOvlyPanelConfig::vencId

VencID of the panel to which this config is to be done.
